    <span class="text-gradient-score-mid" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem;">Vibe Score: 68/100</span>
  </div>
  <p style="color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">The USB Sunset Rainbow Projector ($25.50) is a brilliant budget-friendly ambiance tool that delivers on aesthetic without breaking the bank. If you want gorgeous room vibes on a shoestring, this is genuinely worth it. But here's the honest part: it's not an app-controlled projector. There's no Wi-Fi, no rotation, no "pick any color you want"—just 16 colors that cycle automatically. Perfect for bedroom décor, party backdrops, and TikTok setups. A hidden gem for anyone who values mood lighting over smart home features.</p>
