<p style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem; color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.6;">Your room is boring. Overhead lights are harsh and unflattering. You want that cozy, camera-friendly ambiance you see all over TikTok and Instagram, but you don't want to spend $60+ on a smart projector. Enter the USB Sunset Rainbow Projector—it's the aesthetic shortcut for anyone who values mood over features.</p>

