    <p style="margin: 0; color: var(--foreground); line-height: 1.5;">Grab the USB cable. Plug it into the projector's USB port. Then connect the other end to any USB power source: a phone charger, computer, wall outlet adapter, or power bank. The projector powers on instantly—no buttons, no setup.</p>
